Name: Dark Dimensions: City of Fog Collector's Edition
About the game: Silvertown was swallowed by fog and disappeared from the face of the earth 100 years ago. Search for a town consumed by fog! Unlock forbidden doors and uncover mysterious items in this thrilling Hidden Object Puzzle Adventure game! This is a special Collector's Edition release full of exclusive extras you won’t find in the standard version. The Collector’s Edition includes: Bonus gameplay Built-in Strategy Guide Wonderful Wallpapers Original Soundtrack
